Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.02,0:21:40.80,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}banira soruto de... Burning Love...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.02,0:21:40.80,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sa slanom vanilom... Vatrena ljubav...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.10,0:21:53.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}amai dake nara soruto kakemashou
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.10,0:21:53.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ako je samo slatka, sipajmo malo soli po njoj.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.83,0:22:03.69,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}dare yori mo motto motto watashi wo shitte hoshii kara sarakedashitai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.83,0:22:03.69,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Želim o meni da znaš više, više od bilo koga, želim da ti otkrijem sve o sebi.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.69,0:22:07.10,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}demo dekinai no keiken nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.69,0:22:07.10,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ali ne mogu to da učinim, nemam nikakvog iskustva.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.88,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}modokashi sugiru
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.88,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Tako je frustrirajuće!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.78,0:22:15.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFADA&\3c&H6E6600&}demo amai dake no ai wa chotto
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.78,0:22:15.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H6E6600&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ali ljubav koja je samo slatka...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.55,0:22:23.62,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}watashi ga motomete iru mono to wa chigau
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.55,0:22:23.62,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...se pomalo razlikuje od onoga za čime ja tragam.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.92,0:22:30.70,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}shiro to iwaretara kuro datte icchau
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.92,0:22:30.70,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ako mi kažeš belo, ja odgovaram crno.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.70,0:22:36.30,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF1FCE3&\3c&H486A1D&}sunao ni narenai amanojaku
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.70,0:22:36.30,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H486A1D&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ne mogu da budem iskrena i uvek protivrečim sebi.
